Package org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.publication.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardNotificationService
    Aim of this service whose sole externally accessible method is CardNotificationService.notifyCards(Collection, CardOperationTypeEnum) is to prepare data and notify AMQP exchange of it.
    CardWriteService
    Responsible of Reactive Write of Cards in card mongo collection
    ComputedRecipient
    Recipient computation result data
    ComputedRecipient.BuilderEncapsulator
    Class used to encapsulate builder in order to bypass javadoc inability to handle annotation processor generated classes
    RecipientProcessor
    Allows computation of the three following things for an input Recipient : The list of concerned groups The list of concerned orphan users (concerned users not belonging to any concerned group) The main recipient if any.
